# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:11
translate chinese tammys3_865a31cb:

    # tm "I don't know. I guess it's just fun and I'm good at it. I've never thought about it too much."
    tm "我也不知道。大概是因为这很有趣，而且我做得不错。我从来没想过太多。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:12
translate chinese tammys3_e5f23020:

    # tm "I like the training just as much as the fighting honestly. For different reasons."
    tm "说实话，我喜欢训练和比赛一样多。不过原因不同。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:13
translate chinese tammys3_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "你什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:14
translate chinese tammys3_50887f1d:

    # tm "Well, I like training because it's like I can do a thing that improves me as a person, you know what I mean?"
    tm "嗯，我喜欢训练是因为它让我能做些能让自己变得更好的人，懂我的意思吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:15
translate chinese tammys3_e339f511:

    # tm "Like mentally and physically, I can see places that I can make myself better, then work hard and make it happen."
    tm "比如在身心方面，我能看到自己可以改进的地方，然后努力去实现。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:16
translate chinese tammys3_28ee4347:

    # tm "I like that."
    tm "我喜欢这种感觉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:17
translate chinese tammys3_c191dfaf:

    # tm "There are so many things that you can't change, no matter how hard you work at it, but some things I can."
    tm "世上有很多事无论你多努力都无法改变，但有些事我能改变。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:18
translate chinese tammys3_0d4213c5:

    # tm "Then fighting, I guess it's a way for me to focus my anger and frustrations."
    tm "至于比赛，我想那是我宣泄愤怒和挫败感的一种方式。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:19
translate chinese tammys3_b1b96046:

    # tm "I think that I need that, or else I would be a very angry person."
    tm "我觉得我需要这样，否则我会变成一个非常暴躁的人。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:20
translate chinese tammys3_0f3b895f:

    # pc "What are you angry about?"
    pc "你为什么生气？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:21
translate chinese tammys3_211333e0:

    # tm "Oh man, that's a whole other story that would take a while to tell."
    tm "哦老兄，那又是另一个故事了，说起来得花不少时间。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:22
translate chinese tammys3_28cc3454:

    # tm "But fighting does help with it."
    tm "但比赛确实能帮上忙。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:23
translate chinese tammys3_087b7e28:

    # pc "I see. Well that's cool that you have that outlet to relieve the pressure."
    pc "我明白了。有这种宣泄压力的出口真不错。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/TammyConversations/tammys3.rpy:24
translate chinese tammys3_d6316d2e:

    # tm "Yeah, it definitely helps."
    tm "是啊，确实很有帮助。"

